Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user

Class Faculty

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.User
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.Faculty
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Faculty>
public class Faculty extends User implements Comparable<Faculty>
Represents a Faculty member, including their course load capabilities. Extends the User super class and implements the Comparable interface to compare two Faculty members. The structure is similar to the Student class, but with maxCourses instead of maxCredits.
Author:
Diego Sarria
